# Source data files for imports (not code).
# hats/ holds the OTC hat documents (.docx/.doc/.rtf/.pdf) that were parsed into
# post_writeups and general_hats. They carry members' real names, emails and
# phone numbers — PII that must not enter the repo. They are import INPUTS: the
# text that mattered is in the database, and .vercelignore keeps them off the
# web host too.
hats/
reference/
*.xlsx
*.csv
